{"tid":1316113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【驗證簽文】19年車公簽文預示港人覺醒？Be water?","createTime":"2019-07-14T15:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T15:28:08.000Z","uid":125508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aa907fb3df9f722ada9e5daa2dc0ca64fc5f84e1","tid":1316113,"uid":125508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:28:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20190218/20614696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190218%2F20614696&d=LzMeHrLekQtOmJ7gjClTQJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=e4309672\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190218%2F20614696&h=fbb4831c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20190218/20614696</a><br />\n/八十六籤．中籤<br />\n石田為業喜非常，<br />\n畫餅將來未見香；<br />\n怎曉田耕耘不得，<br />\n那知餅食不充腸。/<br />\n第一句：為有石田耕種而興奮。寓意見眼前甜頭而開心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二句：畫餅幻想香味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；寓意追隨眼前利益收成期，幻想將來發達。<br />\n第三局：呼應首句；石田是沒有生機的，努力耕作是沒用的，空歡喜一場。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第四局：呼應第二句；畫餅充飢，徒勞無功，自欺欺人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">車公預示香港人19年睡醒！是覺醒的時機！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">Be water，不要重複行事，方法持續創新</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>天佑香港，<br />\n天佑義民</strong></span></span>"}]}